properties.description: version of script used to load data

properties.description: config file used to load data. An XML loadspec for MET and vsdb data

properties.description: User contact info, probably email address

properties.name: geo
properties.comments: Contains one or more lat lons

properties.name: subset
properties.description: Similar to "database" in MySQL - a subset or subdivision of the data
